{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RPJ8RtJh3ReCzaQXVpQ9AS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_0129o6GXhQW8iAe9JwRo46gd","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfix: prevent ralph state corruption — reject unknown story keys and skip JSON lines\n\nRoot cause: parseRalphMessage() matched story-completion patterns inside\nstream-json NDJSON lines, creating phantom stories. updateStoryStatus()\nthen blindly created entries for unknown keys via defaultStoryState().\n\nFixes:\n- Skip lines starting with '{' in parseRalphMessage() (JSON envelope)\n- Reject unknown story keys in updateStoryStatus() instead of creating them\n- Add registerStory() for explicit story creation during sprint init\n- Fix state: restore 16-5 through 16-8 to done, remove phantom 1-1-foo\n\nThis bug wasted 13+ sessions (~$20+) in repeated state-corruption fixes.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\" 2>&1","description":"Commit root cause fix and state correction"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":241,"cache_read_input_tokens":55384,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":241},"output_tokens":44,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"329a2c39-c911-452a-8c79-8fa0e53467d5","uuid":"5f00e080-f51b-4b38-98bf-e490de81a11d"}
