{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DJj5hU12AoNhK2EoetSNHk","type":"tool_result","content":"  2830→| **Subagent re-reads are expensive.** | `sprint-state.json` was read 14+ times across 7 sessions. A read cache or single-read-per-session discipline would cut this. |\n  2831→\n  2832→## 7. Action Items\n  2833→\n  2834→| # | Action | Priority | Owner | Status |\n  2835→|---|--------|----------|-------|--------|\n  2836→| 1 | ~~Fix `parseRalphMessage()` to skip JSON lines~~ | CRITICAL | Dev | **DONE — session 22** |\n  2837→| 2 | ~~Make `updateStoryStatus()` defensive~~ | CRITICAL | Dev | **DONE — session 22** |\n  2838→| 3 | **Add circuit breaker for repeated identical state fixes** | HIGH | Dev | OPEN — carried from session 15 |\n  2839→| 4 | **Add ralph sprint-complete termination** | HIGH | Dev | OPEN — carried from session 9 |\n  2840→| 5 | **Clean up phantom `1-1-foo` from sprint-state.json** — set total back to 74, remove the story entry | HIGH | Dev | **NEW** |\n  2841→| 6 | **Clean up cost data** — remove phantom story entries from tracking | MEDIUM | Tooling | OPEN — carried |\n  2842→| 7 | **Convert action items 3-5 to sprint 2 stories** | HIGH | PM | OPEN — carried from session 13 |\n  2843→| 8 | **Reduce \"unknown\" story cost bucket** — $136.52 (20.6%) unattributed | LOW | Tooling | OPEN — carried |\n  2844→| 9 | **Add integration test for ralph with stream-json output containing story patterns** | MEDIUM | QA | **NEW** |\n  2845→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01MsSNN8Vj1Z8bzhRzDEQb55","session_id":"329a2c39-c911-452a-8c79-8fa0e53467d5","uuid":"4d6f7bc8-063a-45d6-b484-13aa337d8640","timestamp":"2026-03-27T15:25:15.192Z"}
